{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "rsv:numbers.33",
    "translationId": "rsv",
    "bookSlug": "numbers",
    "chapterNumber": 33,
    "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33",
    "summary": "Source text for Numbers 33 in Revised Standard Version."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.1",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:1",
      "text": "These are the stages of the people of Israel, when they went forth out of the land of Egypt by their hosts under the leadership of Moses and Aaron.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.2",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:2",
      "text": "Moses wrote down their starting places, stage by stage, by command of the Lord; and these are their stages according to their starting places.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.3",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:3",
      "text": "They set out from Rameses in the first month, on the fifteenth day of the first month; on the day after the passover the people of Israel went out triumphantly in the sight of all the Egyptians,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.4",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:4",
      "text": "while the Egyptians were burying all their first-born, whom the Lord had struck down among them; upon their gods also the Lord executed judgments.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.5",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:5",
      "text": "So the people of Israel set out from Rameses, and encamped at Succoth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.6",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:6",
      "text": "And they set out from Succoth, and encamped at Etham, which is on the edge of the wilderness.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.7",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:7",
      "text": "And they set out from Etham, and turned back to Pi-hahiroth, which is east of Baal-zephon; and they encamped before Migdol.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.8",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:8",
      "text": "And they set out from before Hahiroth, and passed through the midst of the sea into the wilderness, and they went a three days' journey in the wilderness of Etham, and encamped at Marah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.9",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:9",
      "text": "And they set out from Marah, and came to Elim; at Elim there were twelve springs of water and seventy palm trees, and they encamped there.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.10",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:10",
      "text": "And they set out from Elim, and encamped by the Red Sea.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.11",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:11",
      "text": "And they set out from the Red Sea, and encamped in the wilderness of Sin.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.12",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:12",
      "text": "And they set out from the wilderness of Sin, and encamped at Dophkah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.13",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:13",
      "text": "And they set out from Dophkah, and encamped at Alush.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.14",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:14",
      "text": "And they set out from Alush, and encamped at Rephidim, where there was no water for the people to drink.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.15",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:15",
      "text": "And they set out from Rephidim, and encamped in the wilderness of Sinai.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.16",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:16",
      "text": "And they set out from the wilderness of Sinai, and encamped at Kibroth-hattaavah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.17",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:17",
      "text": "And they set out from Kibroth-hattaavah, and encamped at Hazeroth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.18",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:18",
      "text": "And they set out from Hazeroth, and encamped at Rithmah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.19",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:19",
      "text": "And they set out from Rithmah, and encamped at Rimmon-perez.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.20",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:20",
      "text": "And they set out from Rimmon-perez, and encamped at Libnah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.21",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:21",
      "text": "And they set out from Libnah, and encamped at Rissah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.22",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:22",
      "text": "And they set out from Rissah, and encamped at Kehelathah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.23",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:23",
      "text": "And they set out from Kehelathah, and encamped at Mount Shepher.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.24",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:24",
      "text": "And they set out from Mount Shepher, and encamped at Haradah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.25",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:25",
      "text": "And they set out from Haradah, and encamped at Makheloth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.26",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:26",
      "text": "And they set out from Makheloth, and encamped at Tahath.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.27",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:27",
      "text": "And they set out from Tahath, and encamped at Terah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.28",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:28",
      "text": "And they set out from Terah, and encamped at Mithkah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.29",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:29",
      "text": "And they set out from Mithkah, and encamped at Hashmonah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.30",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:30",
      "text": "And they set out from Hashmonah, and encamped at Moseroth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.31",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:31",
      "text": "And they set out from Moseroth, and encamped at Bene-jaakan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.32",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:32",
      "text": "And they set out from Bene-jaakan, and encamped at Hor-haggidgad.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.33",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:33",
      "text": "And they set out from Hor-haggidgad, and encamped at Jotbathah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.34",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:34",
      "text": "And they set out from Jotbathah, and encamped at Abronah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.35",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:35",
      "text": "And they set out from Abronah, and encamped at Ezion-geber.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.36",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:36",
      "text": "And they set out from Ezion-geber, and encamped in the wilderness of Zin (that is, Kadesh).",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.37",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:37",
      "text": "And they set out from Kadesh, and encamped at Mount Hor, on the edge of the land of Edom.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.38",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:38",
      "text": "And Aaron the priest went up Mount Hor at the command of the Lord, and died there, in the fortieth year after the people of Israel had come out of the land of Egypt, on the first day of the fifth month.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.39",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:39",
      "text": "And Aaron was a hundred and twenty-three years old when he died on Mount Hor.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.40",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:40",
      "text": "And the Canaanite, the king of Arad, who dwelt in the Negeb in the land of Canaan, heard of the coming of the people of Israel.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.41",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 41,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:41",
      "text": "And they set out from Mount Hor, and encamped at Zalmonah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.42",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 42,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:42",
      "text": "And they set out from Zalmonah, and encamped at Punon.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.43",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 43,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:43",
      "text": "And they set out from Punon, and encamped at Oboth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.44",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 44,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:44",
      "text": "And they set out from Oboth, and encamped at Iye-abarim, in the territory of Moab.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.45",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 45,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:45",
      "text": "And they set out from Iyim, and encamped at Dibon-gad.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.46",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 46,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:46",
      "text": "And they set out from Dibon-gad, and encamped at Almon-diblathaim.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.47",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 47,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:47",
      "text": "And they set out from Almon-diblathaim, and encamped in the mountains of Abarim, before Nebo.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.48",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 48,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:48",
      "text": "And they set out from the mountains of Abarim, and encamped in the plains of Moab by the Jordan at Jericho;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.49",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 49,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:49",
      "text": "they encamped by the Jordan from Beth-jeshimoth as far as Abel-shittim in the plains of Moab.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.50",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 50,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:50",
      "text": "And the Lord said to Moses in the plains of Moab by the Jordan at Jericho,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.51",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 51,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:51",
      "text": "“Say to the people of Israel, When you pass over the Jordan into the land of Canaan,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.52",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 52,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:52",
      "text": "then you shall drive out all the inhabitants of the land from before you, and destroy all their figured stones, and destroy all their molten images, and demolish all their high places;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.53",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 53,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:53",
      "text": "and you shall take possession of the land and settle in it, for I have given the land to you to possess it.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.54",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 54,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:54",
      "text": "You shall inherit the land by lot according to your families; to a large tribe you shall give a large inheritance, and to a small tribe you shall give a small inheritance; wherever the lot falls to any man, that shall be his; according to the tribes of your fathers you shall inherit.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.55",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 55,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:55",
      "text": "But if you do not drive out the inhabitants of the land from before you, then those of them whom you let remain shall be as pricks in your eyes and thorns in your sides, and they shall trouble you in the land where you dwell.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:numbers.33.56",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 33,
      "verseNumber": 56,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 33:56",
      "text": "And I will do to you as I thought to do to them.”",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
